==Quick overview==

===Everyone===
[[File:Barbarian Assault interface example.png|thumb|The interface for the things you need to use (ear icon), and call (mouth icon).]]
*Calling fast is the most important part of Barbarian Assault. You can call by right-clicking the horn in your inventory. The call changes every 30 seconds.
*The ear icon in the top right corner shows what you need to do, and the mouth icon shows what you need to call for your teammate.
*Avoid running through the middle at the start of a wave, as it causes the penance to run all over the place.
*Attackers and collector run west, healer and defender run east. Try to stay on these sides at the start.
*Between waves, the leader can quick-start the next wave by right-clicking the ladder in the lobbies.
*A second Attacker or Healer is more useful than another Collector or Defender.

===Attacker (red)===
